  "body": "It's extremely common for port 8080 to be in use, why have it as the default?\r\n\r\nThere is no need for Prometheus to be running on port 8080 specifically and it could quite easily run on a different port. This would make it easier to deploy the test network for newcomers.\r\n\r\n",
